'''Battlegrounds Mobile India Pro Series 2026''' or '''BMPS 2026''' is the fifth edition of ''[[Battlegrounds Mobile India Pro Series|Battlegrounds Mobile India Pro Series]]''.

==About==
===Format===
* '''Qualifiers Stage:''''' May 6th - 31st, 2026
** 64 Invited Teams, 4 rounds, 16 matchdays.
** Teams are divided into 4 groups with 16 Teams in each group.
** Each team plays a total of 24 matches (6 matches/round).
** '''Promotion & Relegation System''' is applied. {{TextDropdown|title=For detailed view|section=Prom&Rel|width=max-content}}
* After each round (total 3 rounds), teams are promoted and relagated as follows:
* {{bgcolortext|up|Top 4 Teams}} from Group B, Group C and Group D are promoted to Group A, Group B and Group C respectively.
* {{bgcolortext|stay|5th - 12th ranked Teams}} from each group remains in same.
* {{bgcolortext|staydown|Bottom 4 Teams}} from Group A, Group B, Group C are relegated to Group B, Group and Group D respectively. 
{{TextDropdown|end}} 
** After end of 4th round, {{TextDropdown|title=teams are seeded as follows|section=Qseeds|width=max-content}}
* {{bgcolortext|byeup|Top 8 Teams}} from Group A, qualify for ''Grand Finals.
* {{bgcolortext|up|Bottom 8 Teams}} from Group A, move to ''Semi Finals.
* {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 Teams}} from Group B, qualify for ''Semi Finals.
* {{bgcolortext|stay|Bottom 8 Teams}} from Group B, move to ''Survival Stage.
* {{bgcolortext|stay|All 16 Teams}} from Group C, move to ''Survival Stage.
* {{bgcolortext|stay|Top 8 Teams}} from Group D, qualify for ''Survival Stage.
* {{bgcolortext|down|Bottom 8 Teams}} from Group D, are eliminated. {{TextDropdown|end}} 
{{VerticalMargin}}
* '''Survival Stage:''''' Jun 2nd - 5th, 2026
** 32 Teams from Qualifiers Stage, 4 matchdays.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|8 Teams}} from Group B.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|16 Teams}} from Group C.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|8 Teams}} from Group D.
** Teams are divided into 4 groups with 8 Teams in each group.
** Round-robin format.
** Each team plays a total of 12 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 Teams}} based on the cumulative overall standings advance to ''Semi Finals.
** {{bgcolortext|down|Bottom 24 Teams}} are eliminated.
{{VerticalMargin}}
* '''Semi Finals:''''' Jun 9th - 12th, 2026
** 24 Teams, 4 matchdays.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|8 Teams}} from Qualifiers Group A.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|8 Teams}} from Qualifiers Group B.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|8 Teams}} from Survival Stage.
** Teams are divided into 3 groups with 8 Teams in each group.
** Double Round-robin format.
** Each team plays a total of 16 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 6 Teams}} based on the cumulative overall standings advance to ''Grand Finals.
** {{bgcolortext|stay|7th - 22nd Teams}} (16 teams) proceed to ''Last Chance.
** {{bgcolortext|down|Bottom 2 Teams}} are eliminated.
{{VerticalMargin}}
* '''Last Chance:''''' Jun 13th - 14th, 2026
** 16 Teams, 2 matchdays.
** 12 matches (6 each day).
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 2 Teams}} advance to ''Grand Finals''.
** {{bgcolortext|down|Bottom 14 Teams}} are eliminated.
{{VerticalMargin}}
* '''Grand Finals:''''' Jun 19th - 21st, 2026 at Jaipur Convention Center, {{Flag|in}} Jaipur
** 16 Teams, 3 matchdays.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|8 teams}} from Qualifiers Group A.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|6 teams}} from Semi Finals.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|2 teams}} from Last Chance.
** 18 matches (6 each day).

